15 puzzle is powered by ruby and shoesrb 3 (GUI).

For correct puzzle work  needed:
ruby 1.9.x or older (visit http://www.ruby-lang.org/)
shoesrb 3 (visit http://shoesrb.com/) 

Example of use:

 shoes main.rb

Project branches:

	master - main branch. Just core files.
	windows - branch for maintenance of windows version the game.
	linux - branch for maintenance of linux version the game.
	
For more information please visit http://melnickforever.github.com/15Puzzle/
I hope you will enjoy this app too.

Thanks
Dmitry
